        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Strengths\n",
          "bold": true,
          "color": "red"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "- ",
          "bold": false,
          "color": "red"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "High durability keeps self and the team alive longer in melee centric fights.\n",
          "bold": false,
          "color": "white"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "- ",
          "bold": false,
          "color": "red"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Main weapon is highly disruptive and can make melee fighters weary of engaging.\n",
          "bold": false,
          "color": "white"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "- ",
          "bold": false,
          "color": "red"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Strong AoE healing and buffing capabilities.\n\n",
          "bold": false,
          "color": "white"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Weaknesses\n",
          "bold": true,
          "color": "blue"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "- ",
          "bold": false,
          "color": "blue"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Very prone to high frequency ranged or minion attacks.\n",
          "bold": false,
          "color": "white"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "- ",
          "bold": false,
          "color": "blue"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Lacks a frequent, on demand healing option.\n",
          "bold": false,
          "color": "white"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "- ",
          "bold": false,
          "color": "blue"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Has quite a few niche setups that can be hard to execute, limiting their general purpose abilities.\n",
          "bold": false,
          "color": "white"
        }
